column1: #Text=Over the past few months , the Modern Whig Party has been steadily increasing in membership .
#Text=Around this time last year , the MWP had under 5,000 members .
#Text=Today , that number has grown to nearly 30,000 .
#Text=In your opinion , what is the reason for the MWP 's sudden and rapid increase and popularity ?
#Text=Do you expect it to continue growing at this pace ?
#Text=As the word continues to get out about our organization , we do expect the Modern Whig Party to maintain its steady growth .
#Text=A number of print and broadcast media outlets have even gone so far as to proclaim that the Modern Whig Party is " potentially viable , " and " makes sense .
